Name: On the Hunt
Phase36Description: Haddad, the Iron Wolf Captain, has asked that I be on the lookout for a lone Iron Wolf soldier named Dawood.
Phase62Description: I've found Dawood. He's asked that I help him hunt the criminals that killed his friends.
Phase86Description: Dawood is safe and will be returning to Dahlgur. I should inform Haddad.
Toast: A rogue Iron Wolf hunts an elusive mark.
